name: Nutrition-counter
tagline: Select food items from restaurants and see how many calories there are.
body:
### Nutrition Counter
Count the amount of basic nutrition you're consuming on restaurant menus like Subway using this handy tool. Simply drag the food you want to the top and the progress bars will add up your total number of calories, fat, and protein.

### Questions
Email me at me@alanthai.com for questions.
